#10% loss in value every year loop
# the value will fall until it fall below £1000
#inital value is £3000 in this example 

Currentvalue = int(input("Enter the value of your motorbike!  "))
soldprice = float(Currentvalue)
depriecation = (10 / 100 ) * soldprice
newvalue = soldprice - depriecation


def function():
    print("Year one your motorbike will lose", depriecation, "your new value is", newvalue)
function()

Enter the value of your motorbike!   3000
Year one your motorbike will lose 300.0 your new value is 2700.0
